inns dargestellt.Die Neuauflage umfasst umfangreiche Aktualisierungen, auch mit dem Blick auf die Digitalisierung in der Hotellerie und Gastronomie.  aThis textbook offers a practical presentation of business economics for the successful management of hotels and restaurants, including many examples. Academic experts and business practitioners provide the necessary perspective, furnishing specific answers to many day-to-day issues. The new edition has been extensively updated, particularly regarding the impact of digitization on the hotel and gastronomy industries.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aGastronomiemanagement. 4aHotel-Marketing. 4aHotel-Rechnungswesen. 4aHotelmanagement. 4aLeistungserstellung in der Hotellerie. 4aPersonalwesen in der Hotellerie. 4aWirtschaftsrechtliche Regelungen im Hotel- und Gaststättengewerbe. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Industries / Hospitality, Travel & Tourism.2bisacsh  aHotel and restaurant industry management.  ahotel and restaurant accounting.  ahotel and restaurant marketing.1 aBaier, Martina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBaier, Martina.1 aDahringer, Bernd, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDahringer, Bernd.1 aFrauenrath, Myriam, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrauenrath, Myriam.1 aFuchs, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFuchs, Wolfgang.1 aHansen-Hagge, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHansen-Hagge, Christoph.1 aHeinz Hänssler, Karl, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHänssler, Karl Heinz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHänssler, Markus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relator